OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FDavid Lammy has told JD Vance he was
OL,8,Fwrong to link Henry Nowak's murder to
OL,9,Fimmigration and he warned the US vice-
OL,10,Fpresident the intervention on social
OL,11,Fmedia was "not helpful".
OL,13,FThe Deputy Prime Minister said he
OL,14,Fchallenged Mr Vance in a "robust"
OL,15,Fphone call on Saturday after the US
OL,16,Fpolitician appeared to blame the
OL,17,Fkilling on a "mass invasion" of people
OL,18,Finto Europe.
OL,26,@sD@KOUsD@WO]vD@ZOUvD@aO]yD@NOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
