OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FThe 18-year-old student was handcuffed
OL,8,Fby police who ignored his pleas that
OL,9,Fhe had been stabbed as he lay dying
OL,10,Fafter his British-born killer, Vickrum
OL,11,FDigwa, claimed to have been the victim
OL,12,Fof a racist attack.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer's deputy, who shares
OL,15,Fan unlikely friendship with Mr Vance
OL,16,Fdespite their different political
OL,17,Fbackgrounds, said the two had
OL,18,Fdisagreed about the details
OL,19,Fsurrounding the murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
