PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FMr Lammy, who is also Justice
OL,8,FSecretary, told Sky's Sunday Morning
OL,9,FWith Trevor Phillips: "I spoke to the
OL,10,Fvice-president yesterday and I wanted
OL,11,Fto emphasise a number of things.
OL,13,F"The first is that our democratic
OL,14,Fprocess is working well. This young
OL,15,Fman has been convicted. There is an
OL,16,Finvestigation into the police by the
OL,17,Findependent police complaints
OL,18,Fauthority.
OL,26,@qD@WOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,F"There is an investigation into
OL,8,FHampshire Police by the inspectorate.
OL,9,FThe AG (Attorney General) is looking
OL,10,Fat the sentencing in relation to this.
OL,11,FThe national police chiefs are looking
OL,12,Fat the guidance in relation to this."
OL,14,FHe added: "The second thing was I
OL,15,Fdisagree with him ` this has got
OL,16,Fnothing to do with mass migration.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@eO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,F"This young man (Digwa) was a Brit.
OL,8,FLet's be... clear about that, and I
OL,9,Fsaid, 'Look, Mr vice-president, you're
OL,10,Fwrong about this', and it's also the
OL,11,Fcase that actually murder is coming
OL,12,Fdown in the United Kingdom.
OL,14,F"So, we had an agreeable conversation,
OL,15,Fbut we disagree."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
