PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FIn the latest intervention by the
OL,8,FTrump administration over the murder,
OL,9,FMr Vance had said on Friday: "Henry
OL,10,FNowak died the same way a civilization
OL,11,Fdies: abandoned, handcuffed by
OL,12,Fauthorities who neither trusted nor
OL,13,Fcared for him, and accused of hate
OL,14,Fcrimes he did not commit.
OL,16,F"His murder is as tragic as it is
OL,17,Fenraging.
OL,26,@qD@^OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,F"He should still be alive today, and
OL,8,Fhe would be if the last few
OL,9,Fgenerations of European elites had
OL,10,Fstood their ground against the
OL,11,Fpolitics of self-hatred and the mass
OL,12,Finvasion of migrants, many of whom
OL,13,Fdespise the West and the people who
OL,14,Flove it."
OL,16,FThe vice-president said the response
OL,17,Fto Mr Nowak's death should be
OL,18,F"righteous anger", in a post on X that
OL,19,Fcame after violent unrest in
OL,20,FSouthampton on Tuesday, near the spot
OL,21,Fwhere the teenager was killed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@IO]zD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
