PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FAsked whether he had given Mr Vance a
OL,8,Fticking-off, Mr Lammy said: "We had an
OL,9,Fagreeable conversation because we have
OL,10,Fgot a relationship, but I wanted to
OL,11,Fmake him clear that I disagree with
OL,12,Fsome of the facts that he was
OL,13,Fasserting and to present the facts to
OL,14,Fhim."
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
