PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FHe added: "I also urged him that it's
OL,8,Fnot helpful to tweet in this way,
OL,9,Fpartly because of what the Nowak
OL,10,Ffamily have asked for, and reminded
OL,11,Fhim about their desire not to make
OL,12,Fthis an issue of division and hatred,
OL,13,Fbut to make this an issue of common
OL,14,Fsense."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
