PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FAsked whether he thought the vice-
OL,8,Fpresident had been racist, the Deputy
OL,9,FPrime Minister told the BBC's Sunday
OL,10,FWith Laura Kuenssberg: "I reminded him
OL,11,Fthat the family have called for calm,
OL,12,Fthey don't want division... and, two,
OL,13,FI reminded him also of the online
OL,14,Fspace and how toxic that can become.
OL,15,FSo, we had a robust conversation, a
OL,16,Frespectful conversation.
OL,18,F"We remain colleagues and friends,
OL,19,Fwe're able to do that, and he has
OL,20,Fstrongly-held views."
OL,26,@rD@XOUzD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
