OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FMr Vance's intervention came after the
OL,8,FUS State Department linked "two-tier
OL,9,Fpolicing" to Mr Nowak's death, which
OL,10,FDowning Street has firmly rejected.
OL,12,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,13,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,14,Fstabbing Mr Nowak with a ceremonial
OL,15,Fknife with a 21cm blade, which he
OL,16,Fcarried as part of his Sikh religion.
OL,18,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct is investigating Hampshire
OL,20,FPolice's response in Mr Nowak's case.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
