OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780920676
OL,3,CDavid Lammy told JD Vance 'you're
OL,4,Cwrong' after Henry Nowak case
OL,5,Cintervention
OL,7,FAttorney General Lord Hermer is also
OL,8,Fconsidering whether to refer the
OL,9,Fkiller's sentencing to the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal under the unduly lenient
OL,11,Fscheme, Mr Lammy confirmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
